data.description: There is never a wrong time to buy the right home. Come see for yourself this beautiful 3 bedroom (to up top and one in the basement) end of group townhome in the highly sought after neighborhood of Seven Oaks. This home features numerous updates including NEW ROOF (2023) NEW THOMPSON CREEK WINDOWS (2022)  NEW HVAC (2021) NEW  WATER HEATER (2020) This home has everything you have been looking for from its gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances to its finished basement. Enjoy quiet nights on your oversized deck with a wooded view. Don't forget about the oversized underneath patio off the basement. The neighborhood has its own elementary school, child care center, two clubhouses with pools, onsite tennis courts, playgrounds, common areas, and walking trails. The MARC train is just five minutes down the street with plenty of parking and restaurants such as Ruth's Chris Steak House. The location is a quick five minutes to the Baltimore Washington Parkway, and close proximity to Annapolis, Washington DC, and Baltimore. Arundel Mills Mall and Waugh Chapel Towne Center are just a short 15 minutes away. This is truly a place to call home.
